The main problem with selectable palettes is that you can't have other objects use that palette, unless you also want them to change color. Being able to alter the players color is fine on something like the SNES or the GBA, but not so much here.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=6683">Espozo</a> — Fri Mar 27, 2015 3:28 pm</p><hr />
